<HEADLINE>
<P>
FEDERAL CONTRACT AWARDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Contract Automotive Repair and Maintenance in Burbank won a $711,747 contract 
from the Army for operation of the transportation and motor pools at Ft. 
Stewart and Hunter Army Airfield in Georgia. 
</P>
</TEXT>
