COCAINE; REHABILITATION; CLINICS; ARRESTS -- WASHINGTON DC; HOOKS, BENJAMIN L; 
DRUG ABUSE; NATIONAL ASSOCIATION FOR THE ADVANCEMENT OF COLORED PEOPLE; 
ALCOHOLISM; STING OPERATIONS; POLICE MISCONDUCT; HARASSMENT; BLACKS -- 
POLITICS; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
