at the Vietnamese Temple of Orange County, stands before the Buddha of 
Compassion. MARK BOSTER / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Tom Vo Van lights the 
elaborate altar candles in the Vietnamese Temple. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
